  whatReallyHappened: " KAPALI KAPI C\u0130NAYET\u0130\r\n DAVA\uE092 Yazar Tun\xE7
    Yalman Cinayeti\r\n RAPOR\uE092 Soru\u015Fturma Sonu\xE7 \xD6zeti\r\n Olay\u0131n
    \xD6zeti:\r\n \xDCnl\xFC yazar Tun\xE7 Yalman, yarat\u0131c\u0131 yazarl\u0131k
    kamp\u0131 s\u0131ras\u0131nda konaklad\u0131\u011F\u0131 da\u011F evinde, \r\ni\xE7eriden
    kilitli \xE7al\u0131\u015Fma odas\u0131nda sabah saatlerinde \xF6l\xFC bulunmu\u015Ftur.
    Cesedi, \r\nyard\u0131mc\u0131s\u0131 Bahar taraf\u0131ndan fark edilmi\u015Ftir.
    Olay, klasik \u201Ckapal\u0131 oda\u02EE \r\ncinayetlerindeki gibi gizemli ko\u015Fullar
    alt\u0131nda ger\xE7ekle\u015Fmi\u015Ftir.\r\n Deliller ve Zaman \xC7izelgesi:\r\n
    Yalman\u02BC\u0131n bilgisayar\u0131nda 22\uE09246\u02BCda kaydedilmi\u015F,
    \u201CBu insanlara g\xFCvenemem\u02EE \r\nnotu yer al\u0131r.\r\n Silinmeye \xE7al\u0131\u015F\u0131lm\u0131\u015F
    ses kayd\u0131nda \u201CYapma\u02EE f\u0131s\u0131lt\u0131s\u0131 duyulmu\u015Ftur.\r\n
    Kom\u015Fular 23\uE09200 sonras\u0131 y\xFCksek sesler duymu\u015Ftur.\r\n Oda
    i\xE7eriden kilitlidir, ancak Bahar\u02BC\u0131n \xE7antas\u0131nda yedek anahtar
    bulunmu\u015Ftur.\r\n Cinayet silah\u0131 olarak kullan\u0131lan ve Kerem\u02BCe
    ait \xF6zel bask\u0131 kitap \xFCzerinde \r\nKerem\u02BCin parmak izleri vard\u0131r.\r\n
    \xD6l\xFCm saati 23\uE09200\uE08900\uE09200 aras\u0131, \xF6l\xFCm nedeni ba\u015Fa
    al\u0131nan darbe (kitapla).\r\n Ses kayd\u0131, adli bili\u015Fimce k\u0131smen
    kurtar\u0131lm\u0131\u015F; Tun\xE7\u02BCun sesi tespit edilmi\u015Ftir.\r\n
    2\r\n Senaryo Sonu\xE7lar\u0131\r\nTan\u0131k \u0130fadeleri ve \xC7eli\u015Fkiler:\r\n
    Bahar: Cesedi camdan bakarak g\xF6rd\xFC\u011F\xFCn\xFC s\xF6yler, fakat \xE7antas\u0131nda
    bulunan \r\nyedek anahtar\u0131 neden kullanmad\u0131\u011F\u0131n\u0131 a\xE7\u0131klayamaz.\r\n
    Deniz: Gece hi\xE7bir \u015Fey duymad\u0131\u011F\u0131n\u0131 iddia eder, ancak
    kom\u015Fular\u0131n duydu\u011Fu \r\ny\xFCksek sesleri duymam\u0131\u015F olmas\u0131
    mant\u0131ks\u0131zd\u0131r.\r\n Kerem: Kitab\u0131n kendisine ait oldu\u011Funu
    kabul eder ama cinayetle ilgisi \r\nolmad\u0131\u011F\u0131n\u0131 s\xF6yler.
    Ancak kitap olay yerinde kanl\u0131 bulunmu\u015Ftur.\r\n Lale: \xC7al\u0131\u015Fma
    odas\u0131n\u0131n \u0131\u015F\u0131\u011F\u0131n\u0131 22\uE09230\u02BCda g\xF6rd\xFC\u011F\xFCn\xFC
    belirtir. Bu ifade, \r\nbilgisayardaki son kay\u0131t saatiyle tutarl\u0131d\u0131r.\r\n
    Su\xE7un \xC7\xF6z\xFCm\xFC ve Failin Belirlenmesi:\r\n Yap\u0131lan teknik analizler
    ve tan\u0131k ifadeleri sonucu Bahar\u02BC\u0131n su\xE7lu oldu\u011Fu \r\nbelirlenmi\u015Ftir.\r\n
    Yedek anahtarla oday\u0131 d\u0131\u015Far\u0131dan kilitleyerek \u201Ckapal\u0131
    oda\u02EE izlenimi yaratm\u0131\u015Ft\u0131r.\r\n Cesedi g\xF6r\xFCnce camdan
    bakmas\u0131, normalde anahtar\u0131 kullanmas\u0131 beklenirken \r\n\u015F\xFCphelidir.\r\n
    Bilgisayardaki ses kayd\u0131n\u0131 silmeye \xE7al\u0131\u015Fm\u0131\u015F,
    bu da delilleri yok etme \xE7abas\u0131na \r\ni\u015Farettir.\r\n Kerem\u02BCin
    kitab\u0131n\u0131 cinayet silah\u0131 olarak kullanarak su\xE7 y\xF6nlendirmesi
    yapm\u0131\u015Ft\u0131r.\r\n Tun\xE7\u02BCun son notu, en yak\u0131n\u0131ndakilere
    duyulan g\xFCvensizli\u011Fe i\u015Faret eder.\r\n Olas\u0131 Motif:\r\n Tun\xE7\u02BCun
    yeni kitab\u0131nda Bahar\u02BC\u0131n ge\xE7mi\u015Fine dair baz\u0131 s\u0131rlar\u0131
    if\u015Fa edece\u011Fi ve bunun \r\nBahar\u02BC\u0131n kariyerine zarar verece\u011Fi
    d\xFC\u015F\xFCn\xFClmektedir. Bahar, bu bilgilerin a\xE7\u0131\u011Fa \r\n\xE7\u0131kmas\u0131n\u0131
    \xF6nlemek i\xE7in cinayeti i\u015Flemi\u015Ftir.\r\n Sonu\xE7:\r\n Bahar, \u201Ckasten
    adam \xF6ld\xFCrme\u02EE su\xE7uyla tutuklanm\u0131\u015F ve hakk\u0131nda a\u011F\u0131rla\u015Ft\u0131r\u0131lm\u0131\u015F
    \r\nm\xFCebbet hapis cezas\u0131 istemiyle dava a\xE7\u0131lm\u0131\u015Ft\u0131r.
    Olay, ironik bir \u015Fekilde Tun\xE7\u02BCun \r\nromanlar\u0131nda s\u0131k\xE7a
    i\u015Fledi\u011Fi \u201Ckapal\u0131 oda cinayeti\u02EE temas\u0131n\u0131 yans\u0131tmaktad\u0131r"
